Class SamlPrincipal

java.lang.Object

java.security.Principal
public class SamlPrincipal
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.security.Principal

The SamlPrincipal holds a value for validated user. There are few helpers method to set/get SamlPrincipal from HttpServletRequest. The session attribute key is "saml-principal". Please make sure it is not used for other purpose.
